# UI Assets Directory

Place your user interface images here:

## Suggested UI Assets

- `backgrounds/` - Background images
  - `landing-bg.jpg` - Landing page background
  - `game-bg.jpg` - Game room background
  - `pattern-green.png` - Green pattern texture
- `buttons/` - Custom button images (if not using CSS)
- `avatars/` - Default avatar images
  - `avatar-placeholder.png`
  - `default-user.svg`
- `decorations/` - Decorative elements
  - `border-gold.png`
  - `frame-classic.png`
- `loading/` - Loading animations
  - `spinner.gif`
  - `loading-dice.png`

## Format Recommendations

- Use JPG for photographic backgrounds
- Use PNG for UI elements with transparency
- Use SVG for simple decorative elements
- Consider WebP format for better compression
